description:
TITLE : the system Rose, a general economic equilibrium model

REFERENCES :

From the POSSO test suite.

This has been presented as a general economic equilibrium model in

 Shoven :"Applied general equilibrium modelling",
 IMF Staff Papers, pages 394-419, 1983

and discussed in

  Rose, M., Gebauer, R., Kredel, H. and Kungl, H.:
  "Exemplifying the workability of the Buchberger algorithm for
   computation of general equilibrium by a model published
   in Shoven (83)".
  Department of Economics and Applied Mathematics, University of Heidelberg.
